    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-ix/section-901"
             temporalId="sSection 901">
      <num>Section 901</num>
      <heading>Appropriations</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The council shall include in the annual budget such appropriations of funds as in
               its opinion shall be sufficient for the efficient and proper functioning of such boards
               and commissions.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
